Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.28,0:00:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准备搬往月球的残骸课内…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.22,0:00:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个不要了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.95,0:00:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉维 搬家准备如何了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.22,0:00:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行李比想像的要少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.03,0:00:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一些基本物资 第三事业部的残骸课里也有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.56,0:00:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？那剩下的交给你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.93,0:00:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.60,0:00:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总务课
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.63,0:00:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得拜托他们照顾动物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.60,0:00:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有人事课
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.64,0:00:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小八的辞职书得送上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.97,0:00:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,利用休假制度混到现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.88,0:00:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来已经到极限了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.75,0:00:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经过了那么久吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.35,0:00:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小八走了后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.05,0:00:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过听说小八进展到第三次测验了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.89,0:00:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听说是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.26,0:00:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,闯过这关就合格了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.56,0:00:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两万人中的十八人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.96,0:00:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会成为第一次登上木星的人类吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.70,0:01:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小八原来那么厉害啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.80,0:01:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为周围的人太优秀 所以忽略了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.64,0:01:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像费、里加路多、课长之类的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.27,0:01:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会很寂寞吧？整整七年啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.38,0:01:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,寂寞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.32,0:01:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小八合格后让他签个名吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.39,0:01:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,装饰在残骸课里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.99,0:01:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那让他写大点吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.72,0:01:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能卖个好价钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.46,0:01:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卖的出去吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.66,0:01:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.79,0:01:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟是首次登陆木星的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.16,0:01:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那能写书吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.07,0:01:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菲力普·麦亚兹怎么把部下送上木星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.07,0:01:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能写能写
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.24,0:01:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了 小八去木星之前拍卖他的东西吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.08,0:01:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,头带八商品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.01,0:01:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,商品？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.01,0:01:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帽子和T恤之类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.78,0:01:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个怎么样？小八带的那种头带
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.89,0:01:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,课长好主意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.09,0:01:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个给我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.19,0:02:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小八的特征就属那个了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.53,0:02:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,写首歌吧 「残骸工前往木星」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.20,0:02:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把头带八请到卡拉OK偷偷录音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.87,0:02:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会生气吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.84,0:02:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的 反正头带八有七年不在地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.34,0:02:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等过了七年 都已经生米煮成熟饭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.24,0:02:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.61,0:02:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就等小八通过考试了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.01,0:02:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 他是实战型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.68,0:02:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人偶 人偶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.42,0:02:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾德露在吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.66,0:02:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小八人偶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.80,0:02:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该必有的吧？人偶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.93,0:02:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 人偶应该也不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.40,0:02:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请不要做等身大的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.20,0:02:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
